{"tid":2461403,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"青山山火焚燒逾25小時 飛行服務隊掟水彈撲救仍未救熄","createTime":"2021-03-25T11:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T11:54:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d552ef950dc5b0d0085a93a958b9f852c1e43279","tid":2461403,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T11:39:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mE05JHgjlALmXCRylogM1zk8BeQ=/802x493/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XF54XDVFCRC4RFU5FCHN5ZNZCA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmE05JHgjlALmXCRylogM1zk8BeQ%3D%2F802x493%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXF54XDVFCRC4RFU5FCHN5ZNZCA.jpg&h=f0be7098&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屯門青山昨午（24日）4時53分發生山火，火勢非常猛烈，冒出大量濃煙，多名消防上員登山撲火，飛行服務隊亦派出直升機到場協助。至今午（25日）山火燃燒超過24小時，現場仍火光熊熊，一度出現兩條長約200米的火線，及後飛行服務隊直升機在場投擲水彈協助救火。<br />\n<br />\n至傍晚時分，火線只餘一條近龍鼓灘位置往下白泥方向的火龍，約30米長，暫時無人受傷亦毋須疏散。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210325/K6E4LV6XGRBLTD6DQRMQFNA5HA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210325%2FK6E4LV6XGRBLTD6DQRMQFNA5HA%2F&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2FoeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=a31415ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210325%2FK6E4LV6XGRBLTD6DQRMQFNA5HA%2F&h=853c575e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210325/K6E4LV6XGRBLTD6DQRMQFNA5HA/</a>"},{"pid":"e843db16ba7f5ded173d94f897347cb56e3c14b7","tid":2461403,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T11:43:30.000Z","msg":"青山腹地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本身都少樹"},{"pid":"9749bfa6d0e9e163fe4c3546453867436c6b6d96","tid":2461403,"uid":354471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03